---
import Layout from "../../Layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header/Header.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Pol Gubau Amores - Frontend-Stack Developer and UX designer"
  description="I'm a full-stack developer and UX designer based in Barcelona with +5 years of experience. I love to create beautiful and functional websites and apps."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="px-8 flex gap-8 flex-col">
    <h3
      class="text-xl sm:text-3xl text-center bg-primary p-4 rounded-3xl"
      style={{
        textWrap: "balance",
      }}
    >
      A pixel perfectionist, even though I work with vectors. 🎨👨‍💻
    </h3>
    <p>
      I'm a pixel perfectionist and a passionate software developer and UX
      designer with 5 years of experience. I specialize in web development and
      have worked on various projects, ranging from small websites to
      large-scale web applications. My goal is to create seamless digital
      experiences that merge aesthetics with functionality.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
